      <article class="left">
        <h4>How much bandwidth will I need?</h4>
        <p>That depends! The more images and assets your site has, the more bandwidth you'll use serving up your site.
          The more traffic your site gets, the more bandwidth you'll use.</p>
        <p>As a rough guide, the average bandwidth for a Forge site is about <em>1GB</em> per month. That means you could host 10 sites on our Basic plan and still not be charged for extra bandwidth. Nice!</p>
      </article>

      <article class="right">
        <h4>How does billing work?</h4>
        <p>Your Forge account is billed as a monthly subscription, with <b>no minimum term</b> so you can cancel, upgrade or downgrade as and when you want to.</p>
        <p>We'll bill your payment method once a month for the base rate as indicated by the plan, along with any additional bandwidth costs you incurred during the month.</p>
      </article>

    </div>

